args: After discovering the existence of a group taking\nmoney from women through fake marriages,\nAoi sets out to defeat them.
Eventually, her investigation leads to their\nhideoutâ€”and with her friends at her side,\nshe decides to settle the score for good.
Hear me, evildoers! Today is the day\nI dispense your final justice!
I am the ninja bride Aoi, known across the\nland as a friend of brides and an enemy to\nall who would do them harm!
I know about all your terrible deeds,\nand I'm here to see you pay!
Behold my exposed horns!\nFollowed by Fine Cutlery!
Damn it, who ARE these guys?!\nThey're wipin' the floor with us!

We ain't even done nothin' wrong!
If ya wanna blame someone, blame
the idiots who were stupid enough
to fall for our clearly obvious con!
Toying with someone's heart is the worst\ncrime you can commitâ€”and you WILL pay!
We owe our success to Aoi's efforts.
Wait a second. Where's the man Aoi\nand I cornered the other day...?
Stay alert, everyone! There's more of them!
Don't try any of that ï¼‚ninja brideï¼‚ crap,\nor I'll snap yer little neck like a twig!
Hang on, Aoi! We'll save ya!
I wouldn't move if I were you,\nunless you waaant...SNAP!
Now cry for mercy! Beg for your life!\nBwaaa ha ha ha ha!
Do you think this is funny?\nI hold your life in my hands!
Oh, I know. You're totally in control.\nMe and my friends are powerless.
But you forgot one very important skill.\nPerhaps the most important one of all...
And that's the anger of all\nthe brides you deceived!
Behold the ultimate technique!\nNinja Bride Skill: Bridal Train!
Take this! And this! And some of THIS!\nIt's what you deserve for trampling\nall over our love!
I sent out my invitations and hired a\nnon-refundable caterer, and I'm going\nto take that money out of your HIDE!
You'll have plenty of time to think about\nall the ways you've wronged us when\nyou're rotting in a dungeon somewhere!
Now do you see the true power\nof a bride's righteous anger?
Once they've begun, no one can stop them.
Mercy! Meeeercy! I'll never do it again!\nPlease forgive me!
I feel SO much better now.
Me too! Also, I think this experience will\nmake me a better judge of character.
I'll never let myself be deceived again!
You got to let out your anger AND we\nsaved the dayâ€”it's the perfect ending!
We turned those guys over to the law,\nso I think we're done here.
Thank you for your help, everyone.
It's you ladies what did the heavy liftin'.\nWe mostly just mopped up afterward.
I tell ya what, thoughâ€”I ain't never\ngonna underestimate a bride again.
I also find myself with a new appreciation\nfor these ninja bride skills.
Strength is just another quality\nthat brides possess in spades.
Even though they act with love\nand kindness, brides are also\nSUPER powerful!
I think those qualities are what inspired\nthe creation of ninja bride skills in the\nfirst place.
There's clearly more to this than I thought.
Oh! Welcome back, master!\nAnd you two, of course.
You really saved us there, Aoi.\nI don't know what we would have\ndone without you.
Oh, but I DO have one question.
I started practicing these new skills to help\nyou, and it honestly hasn't been easy.
Without a doubt. In fact, I think\nyou're more dependable than ever.
And not just when you're catching crooks.\nWe're all lucky to have you around.
In that case, I'm going to redouble\nall of my efforts!
